title: Cuisinart Spice And Nut Grinder SG10 Overview
description:

Features:
• Specially designed stainless steel blades for spice and nut grinding
• Push-top on/off control for simple operation
• Built-in safety interlock prevents operation unless the lis is securely in place
• Bowl holds up to 90 grams
• Heavy-duty motor and stainless steel blades
• Dishwasher-safe lid and removable stainless steel bowl
• Storage lid allows for extra spices to be stored in the grinding bowl
• Nonslip rubber feet
• Instruction/ recipe book
